{
  "id": "69d07e22b718d5ea3eef0bcf",
  "title": "想起の習慣",
  "created": 1775271489,
  "updated": 1776785025,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d07e22b718d5ea3eef0bcf",
      "text": "想起の習慣",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271489,
      "updated": 1775271489
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7909c000000000066aa17",
      "text": " 会話や学習したことを脳内で思い出す行動が習慣化されていること",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776783517,
      "updated": 1776783986
    },
    {
      "id": "69e794d600000000009e7050",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784599,
      "updated": 1776784599
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07f180000000000ef4554",
      "text": " 準備なしにいつでもできる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271704,
      "updated": 1775271837
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07f950000000000ef4555",
      "text": "  スマホを使う行動だと、ポケットを取り出して、アンロックして、アプリを立ち上げるまでに時間がかかる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271829,
      "updated": 1776783411
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07fc30000000000ef4557",
      "text": "   歩行者信号が変わってしまう",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271876,
      "updated": 1775271886
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07fd40000000000ef4558",
      "text": " ながら作業できる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271893,
      "updated": 1775271897
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07fd80000000000ef4559",
      "text": "  皿洗いやお風呂掃除をしながらできる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271897,
      "updated": 1775271923
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07ff40000000000ef455a",
      "text": "  歩きながらできる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271925,
      "updated": 1775271927
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7905d000000000066aa12",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776783454,
      "updated": 1776783454
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7905d000000000066aa13",
      "text": "想起すること",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776783454,
      "updated": 1776784630
    },
    {
      "id": "69e79062000000000066aa14",
      "text": " 最近読んだテキストの内容",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776783459,
      "updated": 1776784626
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7906e000000000066aa15",
      "text": " さっきの会話",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776783471,
      "updated": 1776783508
    },
    {
      "id": "69e794c000000000009e704e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784577,
      "updated": 1776784578
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7945100000000009e7047",
      "text": "想起をやるタイミング",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784466,
      "updated": 1776784582
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7945c00000000009e7048",
      "text": " お風呂に入ってるとき[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784476,
      "updated": 1776784483
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7946200000000009e7049",
      "text": " 散歩してるとき[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784483,
      "updated": 1776784489
    },
    {
      "id": "69e794c800000000009e704f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784585,
      "updated": 1776784585
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7947800000000009e704a",
      "text": "想起しにくいタイミング",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784505,
      "updated": 1776784511
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7947f00000000009e704b",
      "text": " 注目する先が細かく現れるとやりにくい[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784512,
      "updated": 1776784575
    },
    {
      "id": "69e794a000000000009e704c",
      "text": "  料理してるとき",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784546,
      "updated": 1776784932
    },
    {
      "id": "69e794aa00000000009e704d",
      "text": "  掃除機をかけてるとき",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784555,
      "updated": 1776784928
    },
    {
      "id": "69e795f300000000009e7056",
      "text": " いろんなことを思いついてるときはそちらをやって、思い出しをしてない[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784883,
      "updated": 1776785025
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7964b00000000009e7057",
      "text": "  お風呂や散歩で思いつきを取り出してるときはそれが楽しいので思い出しはしてない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784972,
      "updated": 1776785018
    },
    {
      "id": "69e79072000000000066aa16",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776783475,
      "updated": 1776784921
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07e400000000000ef4543",
      "text": "[行動遡行]と似てる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271489,
      "updated": 1775271492
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07e440000000000ef4545",
      "text": " [行動遡行]とは、1つ前の行動を思い出す、それを繰り返してどんどん時間を遡っていくこと",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271492,
      "updated": 1776783431
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07ebc0000000000ef454d",
      "text": " 例えば、いまお風呂にいるとしたら",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271612,
      "updated": 1775271630
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07ecd0000000000ef454e",
      "text": "  お風呂に入る前に脱衣所で服を脱いだ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271629,
      "updated": 1775271645
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07edc0000000000ef454f",
      "text": "  その前にトイレに行った",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271645,
      "updated": 1775271650
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07ee20000000000ef4550",
      "text": "  その前に髪をとかした",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271650,
      "updated": 1775271662
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07ee80000000000ef4551",
      "text": "  その前に部屋から移動して脱衣所に服を持って行った",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271656,
      "updated": 1775271687
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07f080000000000ef4552",
      "text": "  その前に……",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271688,
      "updated": 1775271691
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07e640000000000ef4548",
      "text": " 知った場所",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271525,
      "updated": 1775271526
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07e660000000000ef454a",
      "text": "  どこだっけ[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271526,
      "updated": 1775271528
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07e9b0000000000ef454c",
      "text": "  心の調子を良くするものとしてWeb記事で紹介されていた気がする",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271579,
      "updated": 1775271596
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7951200000000009e7051",
      "text": " [想起の習慣]は",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784659,
      "updated": 1776784721
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7952300000000009e7052",
      "text": "  時間軸を遡るかどうかはどちらでもよく",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784676,
      "updated": 1776784711
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7954900000000009e7053",
      "text": "  思い出すだけでなく、復習の気分でやってる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784714,
      "updated": 1776784759
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7924a000000000066aab9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776783947,
      "updated": 1776783948
    },
    {
      "id": "69e79295000000000066aaba",
      "text": "覚えていることを思い出すばかりで、覚えていないのことに直面することはないから、負けがない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784022,
      "updated": 1776784065
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7958700000000009e7054",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784776,
      "updated": 1776784776
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7958700000000009e7055",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776784776,
      "updated": 1776784776
    },
    {
      "id": "69e79242000000000066aab3",
      "text": "タイトルを変えたい[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776783939,
      "updated": 1776783939
    },
    {
      "id": "69e79242000000000066aab4",
      "text": " 「想起の習慣」とすると、このページで言いたいことと少し違ってしまう",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776783939,
      "updated": 1776783956
    },
    {
      "id": "69e79242000000000066aab5",
      "text": " この文字通りの意味では「思い浮かべることの習慣」になる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776783939,
      "updated": 1776783939
    },
    {
      "id": "69e79242000000000066aab6",
      "text": "  これは少し違ってる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776783939,
      "updated": 1776783939
    },
    {
      "id": "69e79242000000000066aab7",
      "text": " 単に思い浮かべることでなく過去の記憶から引っ張り出してくる復習の事を言いたい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776783939,
      "updated": 1776783939
    },
    {
      "id": "69e79242000000000066aab8",
      "text": " でも「復習の習慣」だと教科書や問題集やノートを使った復習のイメージが呼び起こされるので、これもまた違っている気がする",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776783939,
      "updated": 1776783939
    }
  ]
}